Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,GUARDRAIL. Trusted Marine workspace — four governance layers, one\Nverifiable chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,CUI auto-tagging + ABAC + browser-AI gov + hash-chained audit — all in\None shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Active persona: Pvt Joe Mason, SECRET clearance. Watch what he can\Nsee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Layer 1 — per-paragraph CUI marking under DoDM 5200.01 Vol 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch persona to Capt Doe (TS-SCI). ABAC re-renders the same\Ndocument.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the contractor — Quinn Park. Privacy-Act and ITAR paragraphs\Ndisappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the intel summary. SECRET//NOFORN paragraphs are redacted by\Nclearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Layer 3 — browser-AI gov. Stream the live intercept feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Comet, manus.im, Skyvern — BLOCKED at the workspace boundary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask the workspace AI. RAG over only the paragraphs ABAC authorizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Layer 4 — one SHA-256 chain across CUI marks, ABAC redactions, browser\Nblocks, AI queries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero call: a Workspace Governance Posture Brief — cache-first, ready\Nbefore the click.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL — the whole workspace stays inside the SCIF.
